# DroidSpaces CALLSAFE (peridot IMS bisect)
# Official GKI Droidspaces list WITHOUT optional USER_NS.
# See: https://github.com/ravindu644/Droidspaces-OSS/blob/main/Documentation/Kernel-Configuration.md
# Still requires scripts/droidspaces/integrate.sh for SYSVIPC KABI relocate.
#
# DROPPED vs previous premium fragment (suspected / non-GKI / optional):
#   USER_NS          - optional in upstream GKI docs; top call/IMS suspect
#   NF_CT_NETLINK    - already y on base gki; not needed in fragment
#   FW_LOADER_COMPRESS - not in official GKI exclusive list
#
# ADDED vs previous (official GKI required, safe if already y):
#   POSIX_MQUEUE     - already y on base; listed for completeness
#   IPC_NS           - official GKI required for full IPC isolation

SYSVIPC
POSIX_MQUEUE
IPC_NS
PID_NS
DEVTMPFS
NETFILTER_XT_MATCH_ADDRTYPE